Well, with a smile on my face, I do believe I have seen a man look into himself and see an enlightenment.  Dr. Spatz, I welcome you into the community of understanding.  I personally felt that &quot;If you ain't been there, you can't know&quot;.  But in my personal journey of healing and understanding I learned that there were people who were deeply effected by the war.  All you had to do was live the times.  I have learned that passions tend to cloud my logic and I tend to shoot from the hip at times but there is always my respect of your feelings.  So again, welcome.
